> Whenever a Claude session is nearing its compaction limit (or has simply finished something coherent) the `/handoff` skill generates and commits a markdown file explaining everything it did and talked about. The file persists after compaction, giving you a permanent "daily report" of what was decided and why, readable by future sessions, your manager, or your future self.
